            == System.Utilities: The .NET Toolkit for Every Programmer ==

                -- Introduction --

System.Utilities is a collection of tools that programmers will useful for all 
of their coding activities. It contains tools for simple encryption and 
hashing, extensions to various collections in the .NET Framework, common regex 
validators, and useful data types such as Base2 and HashID. This project will 
continue to be updated by Prospective Software and other contributors with 
their favorite tools and tricks to make everyone's life just a little easier.

